{"tid":1051780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首查返先發現係陳詠謙填嘅歌","createTime":"2019-03-08T00:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T01:35:28.000Z","uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f1250ded2370f05b78d8a5b8b28a02b6074286","tid":1051780,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"迷惘是茫茫人生　我為誰而生<br />\n自己一再博取歡笑卻在抖震<br />\n其實我能成為我　為自由而誕生<br />\n絕不能這樣逆我的心　連喊停片刻都不肯<br />\n<br />\n若我只能成為一刻主角　任性得叫宇宙不準發光<br />\n為我生存立了一支光柱　就這麼　不等誰成就我<br />\n我要成就這刻　讓我飛一趟<br />\n<br />\n真係幾鍾意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b747abe198c302cccb4513df452c4ced72ed1e1","tid":1051780,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:35:37.000Z","msg":"高山低谷<br />\n一雙手"},{"pid":"3f5415f575d8ad211e764dce959812be6a7b70d8","tid":1051780,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"隨風 你說得多麼灑脫<br />\n如何盡如人意 少不免<br />\n何妨盼望永生 等不了"},{"pid":"3d13fa1e4ac457ea8aac8288983a8831e0d98913","tid":1051780,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"非凡人生 <br />\n天才卻被連登仔恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bc1f9d5c6636d422af8dc0b094ea05cba04cf7","tid":1051780,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"芝麻開門"},{"pid":"f5f3899ba7ad23e844849e8ed9cbd90037c8a809","tid":1051780,"uid":199352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d13fa1e4ac457ea8aac8288983a8831e0d98913","tid":1051780,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"非凡人生 <br />\n天才卻被連登仔恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"因為有堆真係填得好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔否認偶爾都有高質作品<br />\n但比起其他填詞人嚟講 垃圾作嘅出現率高